						<div class="postbody">I have a little n00b question regarding the MMC1. When I bankswitch the CHR background like this<br /><br />LDA #%00000010 ;Swap background<br />JSR Background_Select ;Go to $C000 bankswitching subroutine<br /><br />;Rest of code here<br /><br />Background_Select:<br />  STA $C000<br />  LSR A<br />  STA $C000<br />  LSR A<br />  STA $C000<br />  LSR A<br />  STA $C000<br />  LSR A<br />  STA $C000<br />  RTS<br /><br />It works fine on an emulator. However, on real hardware, it seems like there is no such thing, the name entry screen of Deal or no Deal keeps the title background CHR bank. What am I doing wrong?<br /><br />Here are the pics<br /><br />Emu<br /><a href="http://s1074.photobucket.com/user/KilleRotom/media/deal002_zpsd0deb1f2.png.html" class="postlink"><img src="http://i1074.photobucket.com/albums/w408/KilleRotom/deal002_zpsd0deb1f2.png" alt="Image" /></a><br />Real Hardware<br /><a href="http://s1074.photobucket.com/user/KilleRotom/media/vUhk9sC_zps07907766.jpg.html" class="postlink"><img src="http://i1074.photobucket.com/albums/w408/KilleRotom/vUhk9sC_zps07907766.jpg" alt="Image" /></a> (Uses the title screen CHR bank)</div>

					
